9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Y5UiR9&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=d5ad889f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Y5UiR9</a><br />\n<br />\n3️⃣飲食及酒店業職工總會<br />\n都係好簡單，做飲食的手足都可入，你係學生炒下散又好，全職定兼職都入得<br />\n入會表：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/8yK7ZEtZboY45apU7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F8yK7ZEtZboY45apU7&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=f50856d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/8yK7ZEtZboY45apU7</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">入會機會黎喇 <br />\n大學生及兼職打工仔</span></span><br />\n個幾星期 工會人數增長都係得千幾人<br />\n大家踴躍入會 齊齊投票<br />\n入左會先可以公投<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e525fca7cc4746a0d24aec8bd32e39fd66efbe96","tid":2063531,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:25:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6deaf6bb77d09099079ecc9b80b3385fa7139159","tid":2063531,"uid":178909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:39:37.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77393129f9ea0f0f7c3f13857fe8976b107069f3","tid":2063531,"uid":178909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:40:54.000Z","msg":"［三度置頂］突發！614大三罷公投改咗去6月20<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2062463\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2062463</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n公會要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFb IG 連登一齊share<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s